# regenerable artifacts (stitch)
# NOTE: circuit/descriptors/*staged*.tsv are Lean-emitted but include_str!'d at
# compile time, so a fresh clone cannot build dregg-circuit without them. They are
# tracked via Git LFS (see .gitattributes) rather than ignored. Regenerate with
# scripts/emit-descriptors.sh on the Lean host; they change only on VK-epoch flips.
demo/run/*.png
orb/conformance/h2c-host/h2c-host
*.png.skip
wasm/pkg-mwt/
orb/conformance/h2c-host/h2c-host

